name: VELDEN - THROW
description:
- Throw dimensions approximately 100cm x 150cm
- Fabric composition 90% Wool, 10% Cotton Yarn
- All prices are in Australian dollars

As this is a hand woven product no two throws are identical, the images provided are for look and feel only. 

PLEASE NOTE: All throws are hand made to order. We always try and get your product to you as soon as possible, however please allow up to 8 weeks for production of each item.

name: VELDEN
description:
- 40cm x 40cm hand woven cushion 
- Fronts approximately 90% Wool, 10% Cotton Yarn
- Backing colours vary depending availability, the majority of backs are made of 100% natural fibers
- Insert included is 100% duck feather
- Zip at back to allow removal of insert for easy laundering
- All prices are in Australian dollars

As this is a hand woven product no two cushions are identical, the images provided are for look and feel only.
